    "attributes": {
        "action": "Grant an extra UK Bank Holiday to Reunite the Community after Brexit",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Like many families the referendum followed by the Brexit process has split us. This has not been helped by the apparent intransigence of our politicians. My uncle and I, who have opposing views, believe a Bank Holiday would help reconcile society and acknowledge the stress and pain people have had.",
